text: "New Kid in Town" is a 1976 song by the Eagles. It was taken from their fifth studio album Hotel California. It went to number 1 in the United States and Canada, number 6 in New Zealand, number 8 in Spain and number 9 in the Netherlands and Norway. It won a Grammy award. == References == Category:1976 songs Category:Rock songs Category:Eagles (band) songs Category:Trisha Yearwood songs
